==功效==
一些动物试验和体外试验表明大蒜素有[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antibiotics 抗菌]{{Wayback|url=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antibiotics |date=20180313152925 }}<ref>{{cite journal en|last= Ankri |first= S|authorlink= |coauthors= Mirelman D|year= 1999|month= |title= Antimicrobial properties of allicin from garlic |journal= Microbes Infect|volume= 2|issue= |pages= 125–9|id= |url= |accessdate= |quote= }}</ref>、[[抗真菌|抗真菌]]<ref name="Chester" />、[[消炎|消炎]]、[[抗氧化|抗氧化]]<ref>{{cite journal en| author= U. Sela, S. Ganor, I. Hecht, A. Brill, T. Miron, A. Rabinkov, M. [[Meir_Wilchek|Wilchek]], D. Mirelman, O. Lider and R. Hershkoviz | title= Allicin inhibits SDF-1alpha-induced T cell interactions with fibronectin and endothelial cells by down-regulating cytoskeleton rearrangement, Pyk-2 phosphorylation and VLA-4 expression | url= https://archive.org/details/sim_immunology_2004-04_111_4/page/391 | journal= Immunology | volume=111 | year=2004| pages=391–399 | doi= 10.1111/j.0019-2805.2004.01841.x}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en| author=Lindsey J. Macpherson, Bernhard H. Geierstanger, Veena Viswanath, Michael Bandell, Samer R. Eid, SunWook Hwang, and Ardem Patapoutian | title=[http://www.current-biology.com/content/article/fulltext?uid=PIIS096098220500391X The pungency of garlic: Activation of TRPA1 and TRPV1 in response to allicin] | journal=Current Biology | volume=15 | issue=May 24 | year=2005 | pages=929–934}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en| author=Bautista DM, Movahed P, Hinman A, Axelsson HE, Sterner O, Hogestatt ED, Julius D, Jordt SE and Zygmunt PM | title=Pungent products from garlic activate the sensory ion channel TRPA1| journal=Proc Natl Acad Sci USA | volume=102 | issue=34 | year=2005 | pages=12248–52 | doi=10.1073/pnas.0505356102 | pmid=16103371}}</ref>、[[抗血栓|抗血栓]]<ref>{{cite journal en| author= Srivastava KC | title= Evidence for the mechanism by which garlic inhibits platelet aggregation. | journal= Prostaglandins Leukot Med | volume=22(3) | year=1986 | pages=313–321 | doi= 10.1016/0262-1746(86)90142-3 }}</ref>、[[降血压|降血压]]<ref>{{cite journal en| author= Silagy CA, Neil HA | title= A meta-analysis of the effect of garlic on blood pressure | journal= J Hypertens | volume=12(4) | year=1994| pages=463–468 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en| author= A. Elkayam, D. Mirelman, E. Peleg, M. [[Meir_Wilchek|Wilchek]], T. Miron, A. Rabinkov, M. Oron-Herman and T. Rosenthal | title= The effects of allicin on weight in fructose-induced hyperinsulinemic, hyperlipidemic, hypertensive rats | url= https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-hypertension_2003-12_16_12/page/1053 | journal= Am. J. Hypertens | volume=16 | year=2003| pages=1053–1056 | doi= 10.1016/j.amjhyper.2003.07.011}}</ref>、维持[[脂蛋白|脂蛋白]]平衡、防治[[动脉硬化|动脉硬化]]<ref>{{cite journal en| author= S. Eilat, Y. Oestraicher, A. Rabinkov, D. Ohad, D. Mirelman, A. Battler, M. Eldar and Z. Vered | title= Alteration of lipid profile in hyperlipidemic rabbits by allicin, an active constituent of garlic | journal= Coron. Artery Dis.  | volume=6| year=1995| pages=985–990}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en| author= D. Abramovitz, S. Gavri, D. Harats, H. Levkovitz, D. Mirelman, T. Miron, S. Eilat-Adar, A. Rabinkov, M. [[Meir_Wilchek|Wilchek]], M. Eldar and Z. Vered, | title= Allicin-induced decrease in formation of fatty streaks (atherosclerosis) in mice fed a cholesterol-rich diet | journal= Coron. Artery Dis.  | volume=10 | year=1999| pages=515–519 | doi= 10.1097/00019501-199910000-00012}}</ref> 等功效。

一个2007年的临床试验结果是，对于[[胆固醇|胆固醇]]水平较高的病人，大蒜素不能降低血液胆固醇浓度。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Gardner CD, Lawson LD, Block E |title=Effect of raw garlic vs commercial garlic supplements on plasma lipid concentrations in adults with moderate hypercholesterolemia: a randomized clinical trial |journal=Arch. Intern. Med. |volume=167 |issue=4 |pages=346–53 |year=2007 |pmid=17325296 |doi=10.1001/archinte.167.4.346|display-authors=etal}}</ref>

2009年，Vaidya、Ingold 和 Pratt 的研究表明大蒜素的生物功效主要是由大蒜素分解产生的2-丙烯次磺酸造成的，该化合物不稳定，很快便与体内的[[自由基|自由基]]发生反应使之失活。<ref>{{cite journal en|last= Vaidya|first= Vipraja|authorlink= |coauthors= Keith U. Ingold, Derek A. Pratt|year= 2009|month= |title= Garlic: Source of the Ultimate Antioxidants - Sulfenic Acids|journal= Angewandte Chemie|volume= 121|issue= 1|pages= 163-166|id= |doi= 10.1002/ange.200804560|url= http://www3.interscience.wiley.com/cgi-bin/fulltext/121541722/HTMLSTART|accessdate= 21 Feb 2009|quote= }}{{Dead link|date=2019年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

==用途==
提纯的大蒜素可用作[[抗菌药|抗菌药]]、[[饲料添加剂|饲料添加剂]]、[[杀虫剂|杀虫剂]]和[[杀菌剂|杀菌剂]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chemyq.com/xz/xz4/38061jijiv.htm|title=大蒜辣素；蒜素；蒜辣素；大蒜素|publisher=化工引擎|accessdate=2009-09-05|archive-date=2011-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110204050752/http://www.chemyq.com/xz/xz4/38061jijiv.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

